        { "@type": "Question", "name": "How do I replace Elevar for free on Shopify?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "CAPI Shield by Stack Architect replaces Elevar for free. It routes Shopify purchase events server-side to Meta Conversions API and Google Enhanced Conversions via a Make.com webhook, achieving Event Match Quality scores of 7–8.5 — the same technical outcome as Elevar at $225++ per month, at $0 per month. Deploys in 6 minutes with no code required on Make.com's free tier." } },
