        { "@type": "Question", "name": "Is my Shopify data secure with the Stack Architect automation stack?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes. All data stays inside your own Google account and Make.com workspace. Stack Architect has zero access to your Shopify orders, customer data, or ad accounts. The tools are GDPR compliant by design — you own and control everything. Data flows from Shopify to your Make.com account to your Google Sheets, with no third-party storage or intermediary." } },
